{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_91","type":"agent_message","text":"I’m making a second metadata pass now. This one is narrower than the first: it registers `LambdaMapper`, the `AnnotationMapper` serialization hooks, the extra JDK serialization field on `String`, the `Unsafe.theUnsafe` lookup that xstream’s limited unsafe provider performs, and it broadens the `java.lang.Object` constructor registration so the JDK serialization path can actually use it."}}
